  <summary date="2021-09-10T16:37:27Z" status="Introduced in House">Selective Service Repeal Act

This bill repeals the requirement for males between the ages of 18 and 26 to register with the Selective Service. The bill also specifies that an individual shall not be penalized for prior failure to register with the Selective Service.</summary>
